function OnLeaveDepress() local parent = Component.GetProperty("ParentPopup") Component.Call("Root.LuaCall", "ClosePopup", parent) end
function SetParentPopupAddress(addr) print("Setting parent address: "..tostring(addr)) Component.SetProperty("ParentPopup", addr) end

uientry.unicode: To play a rematch, all players must agree to it.||This shows the votes for a rematch.
Before swapping sides, each player must agree to it.||This shows the votes for swapping sides.
When this is selected any messages you send will be sent to all players.||To only send to the players on your team switch to the team button.
